## Step 8 — Helpdesk Join Computers Delegation

Initial attempt (failed):

dsacls "OU=2.NB_Computers,DC=northbridge,DC=local" /I:T /G "northbridge\DLG_Helpdesk_Join_Computers:CA;Validated write to DNS host name"  
dsacls "OU=2.NB_Computers,DC=northbridge,DC=local" /I:T /G "northbridge\DLG_Helpdesk_Join_Computers:CA;Validated write to service principal name"  

Image: images/08-0-validatewrerror.png  

Correct approach:

dsacls "OU=2.NB_Computers,DC=northbridge,DC=local" /I:T /G "northbridge\DLG_Helpdesk_Join_Computers:CC;computer"  
dsacls "OU=2.NB_Computers,DC=northbridge,DC=local" /I:T /G "northbridge\DLG_Helpdesk_Join_Computers:DC;computer"  

Validation:

dsacls "OU=2.NB_Computers,DC=northbridge,DC=local" | Select-String "DLG_Helpdesk_Join_Computers" -Context 0,5  

Images:  
images/08-1-helpdesk-join-computers-delegation.png  
images/08-2-helpdesk-join-computers-delegation-filter.png  

